      <title>伊朗选出希望与西方重启核谈判的总统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-06/reformist-pezeshkian-elected-president-of-iran-state-tv</link>
      <description><![CDATA[69 岁的心脏外科医生马苏德·佩泽什基安 (Masoud Pezeshkian) 希望与美国重启具有里程碑意义的核协议谈判，他在这场突显伊朗国内外面临的重大挑战的选举中当选为伊朗总统。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-06/reformist-pezeshkian-elected-president-of-iran-state-tv</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Jul 2024 03:18:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Cleanp 将在珠穆朗玛峰最高营地工作数年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-07-06/mount-everest-s-highest-camp-is-littered-with-frozen-garbage-and-cleanup-is-likely-to-take-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加德满都尼泊尔（美联社）——据一位夏尔巴人称，世界最高峰的最高营地上到处都是垃圾，需要几年时间才能清理干净，他带领一支队伍清理了珠穆朗玛峰峰顶附近的垃圾并挖出了被冰冻多年的尸体。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-07-06/mount-everest-s-highest-camp-is-littered-with-frozen-garbage-and-cleanup-is-likely-to-take-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Jul 2024 03:09:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
